The_Parole_Officer http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Parole_Officer 0 The Parole Officer is a 2001 British comedy film, directed by John Duigan. It was the first feature film to star comedian Steve Coogan. The film follows a diverse group of former criminals as they assist their probation officer in proving his innocence after a murder accusation.
